{"tid":903611,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【果迷注意】升級IOS 12.1 iPhone X過熱爆炸","createTime":"2018-11-15T16:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T07:23:00.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b27e67ecc9602e42237c5d3b04567ca311e4c5","tid":903611,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2018/11/1542274056_5i-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2018%2F11%2F1542274056_5i-1280w.png&h=948d7648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niPhone X出現過熱爆炸事件，美國華盛頓一名用戶周二在Twitter向蘋果投訴，其iPhone X於升級IOS 12.1時過熱爆炸，並附上爆炸後的圖片，可見機身嚴重損壞。事主Rahel Mohamad向網站Gadgets360稱，出事iPhone X今年1月買，使用以來一直未有出現問題，而於升級進行時，其iPhone X接駁著原廠的充電器和充電線，更新完成後，他拔掉充電線拿起，但太燙手，他立即放下，未幾機身開始冒煙，並且起火。蘋果已要求Mohamad將iphone送回給他們檢查，又指無收到iPhone X廣泛出現過熱事故。有人揣測是鋰電池有缺陷，引致過熱<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E6%9E%9C%E8%BF%B7%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E3%80%91%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9Aios-12-1-iphone-x%E9%81%8E%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8-150035\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%259E%259C%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2584%258F%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%258D%2587%25E7%25B4%259Aios-12-1-iphone-x%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2582%25B8-150035&d=w6KT%2BKEW50acgijZ%2FDEmhcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=833e387b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E6%9E%9C%E8%BF%B7%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E3%80%91%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9Aios-12-1-iphone-x%E9%81%8E%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8-150035</a>"},{"pid":"36e60c801c0567cd78f2363358b8b9027c1445e1","tid":903611,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:32:22.000Z","msg":"用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35310d67a314e54c215b7c66cc3